sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant DB as Postgres/PostGIS
    participant Worker
    participant Sources
    participant Reviewer

    User->>API: submit parcel/polygon + intent
    API->>DB: create area + report_run
    API->>Worker: enqueue feature extraction
    Worker->>DB: resolve source manifest
    Worker->>Sources: fetch/cache source data if needed
    Worker->>DB: write evidence observations
    Worker->>DB: execute rules/write claims/tasks
    Worker->>DB: compile report sections
    Reviewer->>DB: review/approve/annotate
    API->>User: deliver dossier + JSON
